<br>
But it is possible and rather simple.. buff yourself up with phantom buff spell (you will need the little regen it gives) and just tank a little.. the mob will almost always turn on you and letting the rogue get some backstabs.<br>
<br>
I don't know if it works at high levels but it works rather nice at lvl 27. <br>
<br>
Probably you will get more XP solo the in this way but it is more fun then soloing all the time.<br>
